attributionInfo.brokerName: D R Horton Realty of Melbourne

data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA MORTGAGE.  Charming private oasis w contemporary open floor plan. Cozy fireplace, easy care floors, split bedroom plan, screened lanai. Plenty of options for dining room or enjoy the large breakfast bar. Kitchen has updated appliances and plenty of cabinets. Built in entertainment area adds even more space.  Mixture of tropical and shady oaks canopy the serene yard which backs up to preserve/canal. Hardiplank siding too! Cul-de-sac street perfect for a stroll.  Side entry garage w/ plenty of driveway space. Convenient to Sebastian River, Vero Beach. NO HOA. Room for all the toys!
